form.name: description
form.value: Fast & easy computing Perfect budget laptop for students and working professionals that helps get jobs done quickly and efficiently thanks to the Intel Core i5-1135G7 processor. The latest Extensa Acer Laptop has been redesigned to be thinner and lighter than ever. With less than 20mm thin and with a weight of around 1.7kg, it can accompany you wherever you need to go The Extensa 15 will help improve your all-round video conferencing experience. It maintains a strong, consistent wireless signal with the strategically placed Wi-Fi 5 (802.11ac) wireless antenna and MU-MIMO. It also offers battery life upto 8 hours. Ease of storage: 4 GB of onboard DDR4 system memory, 4 GB of system memory with 512 GB SSD helps easily store and share important projects and data; The Laptop comes with Windows 11 Home and 1 year International Travellers Warranty.Call 1800-11-6677 to reach out to Acer customer support team for any queries Resolution: 1080p1280 X 720; Display Resolution Maximum: 1920 X 1080; Software Included: Webcam
